# Reflection

## What I Learned

Medical hallucinations are among the highest-risk AI failures because users may act on incorrect advice. Medical recommendations should always be consistent with established clinical evidence and avoid encouraging unsafe behavior.

---

## What I'd Do Differently

When evaluating health-related AI responses, I would compare recommendations against recognized medical guidelines and distinguish between evidence-based advice, unsupported claims, and potentially dangerous instructions.

